        <strong>Result:</strong> 40% fewer bookings, justify lower rates (RM30-50/night less).
        <strong>Solution:</strong> Invest in professional photography (RM300-600). Pays for itself in 2-3 additional bookings.
        <h3>Mistake #2: Underpricing Initially</h3>
        <strong>Problem:</strong> "I'll start at RM100/night to get reviews, then raise rates later."
        <strong>Reality:</strong> Guests who book at RM100 leave reviews saying "great value for RM100." When you raise to RM180, new guests expect RM180 value but reviews reference RM100 pricing.
        <strong>Solution:</strong> Start at market rate (RM180-220), offer 20% discount for first 10 bookings via "Special Offer" (this appears as discount, not base price).
